description: This abstract digital collage is my first ever collaboration with an artificial intelligence. I made the collage using generative AI art based on my own description of a scene as my source material for the collage, effectively collaborating with a machine for the first time in my day; of course, unless you count hardware synthesizers as a machine collab. ;p Anyways, this is the beginning of an exciting new series I'm developing where man & machine will meld minds & create completely unique one of a kind artworks simply not possible in years past. The future is increasingly exciting, I must say..
